00:52:33.710 --> 00:52:40.240
And this can be anything that
really fits the theme of your game.

00:52:42.830 --> 00:52:46.300
So this is what this looks like in code.

00:52:46.530 --> 00:52:49.820
First, we're going to want
to call-- we'll do it,

00:52:49.920 --> 00:52:51.980
for instance, on the local player.

00:52:52.040 --> 00:52:56.540
We'll load a photo with size,
and we offer a couple of different sizes,

00:52:56.580 --> 00:52:58.960
and then we'll pass
in a completion block.

00:52:59.030 --> 00:53:04.580
This completion block will then hand
you a photo and an impossible error.

00:53:04.990 --> 00:53:09.250
And then all you need to do is
set whatever your image is to

00:53:09.260 --> 00:53:11.870
